h4 Any player
p
    | When any opposing player moves into an adjacent hex, a player with this 
    | ability may immediately choose to turn and face their opponent. This happns
    | before any 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SLAM}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]} 
    | or 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.STEAL}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.STEAL]} 
    | action is resolved, or before the opposing player moves any further.
p
    | Note that this action does not stop the opposing player's action.